    },
    {
      "blocks": [
        {
          "target_block_id": "lrtb_ad5765472639964618962a32",
          "text": {
            "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
            "qa_status": "passed",
            "text": "添加角色和背景",
            "text_hash": "389a1ba5f40d984006196e080425e6778a727f6b89813db0e4380107b50c5c63",
            "variant_version_id": "lrzv_d3e5da6954d51fb01b9c6387"
          },
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "target_block_id": "lrtb_446ae44a7d220066a552d8c8",
          "text": {
            "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
            "qa_status": "passed",
            "text": "开始一个新的 Scratch 项目，并添加一个角色精灵和一个背景。",
            "text_hash": "c4c379512ac2456018c54ac57c75ee32f46760db6eadc93788b90da40410833a",
            "variant_version_id": "lrzv_d3e5da6954d51fb01b9c6387"
          },
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "target_block_id": "lrtb_6087e68b907a063eda279dab",
          "text": {
            "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
            "qa_status": "passed",
            "text": "[!TASK]\n在新标签页中打开一个新的 Scratch 项目{:target=\"_blank\"}。打开后带有 Scratch 猫的项目就是正确的起点。",
            "text_hash": "3ee8c08f487940ae99774fce6113004bf94a48a1340ded94623dac760837f178",
            "variant_version_id": "lrzv_d3e5da6954d51fb01b9c6387"
          },
          "type": "quotation"
        },
        {
          "target_block_id": "lrtb_7699e80dec6fc4e4672bdfa1",
          "text": {
            "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
            "qa_status": "passed",
            "text": "[!TASK]\n删除猫精灵。\n使用缩略图上的垃圾桶图标删除精灵。",
            "text_hash": "d41abf114f0eb0da57453b7f31032c15019df32500c1feeb1d0170c74738fa5e",
            "variant_version_id": "lrzv_d3e5da6954d51fb01b9c6387"
          },
          "type": "quotation"
        },
        {
          "target_block_id": "lrtb_a24f7b1522a74db70a79b1c1",
          "text": {
            "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
            "qa_status": "passed",
            "text": "[!TASK]\n使用 **选择一个精灵** 添加任意角色。本示例使用 Giga Walking，但你的角色可以按照你的喜好显示。\nScratch 编辑器右下角的“选择一个精灵”按钮。",
            "text_hash": "a8d56baa6950b21b7ac2522058c85ef945d8f29ce4039d052947f75662973cb8",
            "variant_version_id": "lrzv_d3e5da6954d51fb01b9c6387"
          },
          "type": "quotation"
        },
        {
          "target_block_id": "lrtb_48f791c6914a95965e1696f2",
          "text": {
            "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
            "qa_status": "passed",
            "text": "[!TASK]\n使用 **选择一个背景** 添加任意背景。本示例使用 Desert，但请选择适合你的游戏的场景。\nScratch 编辑器右下角的“选择一个背景”按钮。",
            "text_hash": "cae15a3be94519e32a3b92efcb6bd3550f182923cb67ef9e4c9c33f21a9442a2",
            "variant_version_id": "lrzv_d3e5da6954d51fb01b9c6387"
          },
          "type": "quotation"
        },
        {
          "target_block_id": "lrtb_b97ae95642ccf79b5c61b7d2",
          "text": {
            "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
            "qa_status": "passed",
            "text": "[!TASK]\n将角色放在舞台底部附近。\nGiga Walking 精灵。{:width=\"100px\" height=\"100px\" style=\"object-fit: contain;\"}",
            "text_hash": "7ab784b8da5d286680285cf1b3b7ec0e7dee16753a1f1b3c77e4825fc720bbc3",
            "variant_version_id": "lrzv_d3e5da6954d51fb01b9c6387"
          },
          "type": "quotation"
        },
        {
          "target_block_id": "lrtb_4431a2f21c6445a22f33be55",
          "text": {
            "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
            "qa_status": "passed",
            "text": "[!TASK]\n选择角色并点击 **代码** 选项卡。添加这些积木来设置它的位置、方向和大小。\nblocks3\n+当绿旗被点击\n+显示\n+移到 x: (-100) y: (-70)\n+面向方向 (90)\n+将大小设为 (100) %\n这些值会将示例角色放在靠近地面的位置。如果你的角色或背景不同，请调整位置和大小。",
            "text_hash": "7322e8fd08549bd1fb0ac1ac64331b4b85ba23fca3e85b7f70ac61a6ce1d8009",
            "variant_version_id": "lrzv_d3e5da6954d51fb01b9c6387"
          },
          "type": "quotation"
        },
        {
          "target_block_id": "lrtb_d8c1d06bebda6e7eb10c013b",
          "text": {
            "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
            "qa_status": "passed",
            "text": "[!TIP]\n这是你的**起始状态**。在游戏开始前点击绿旗时，它会重置。",
            "text_hash": "363367487eaf139deee4439397dd124cc5835af5cc3ca264eff9b545c7758af3",
            "variant_version_id": "lrzv_d3e5da6954d51fb01b9c6387"
          },
          "type": "quotation"
        },
        {
          "target_block_id": "lrtb_674fd19c7acdb538340c9f18",
          "text": {
            "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
            "qa_status": "passed",
            "text": "[!TASK]\n**测试你的项目。** 每次点击绿旗时，角色都应该出现在同一个位置。",
            "text_hash": "9e05951e3736df63645dd5e2058f58ffc0f936958457fb804fd3ed66068c8302",
            "variant_version_id": "lrzv_d3e5da6954d51fb01b9c6387"
          },
          "type": "quotation"
        }
      ],
