    },
    {
      "blocks": [
        {
          "target_block_id": "lrtb_be09c2677043d6ea18c83659",
          "text": {
            "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
            "qa_status": "passed",
            "text": "让角色跳跃",
            "text_hash": "8d41de91dc964284b94ccbaf3f92c60c261ea71fc4dd8466dd3d93f9a6bdeb60",
            "variant_version_id": "lrzv_f40d76f6df22e368fb8ecb6c"
          },
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "target_block_id": "lrtb_b068bec472d5f8209243509b",
          "text": {
            "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
            "qa_status": "passed",
            "text": "让角色向上跳起，然后落回同一个位置。",
            "text_hash": "ccbb791f8577a37a1f8e6a30af5e087e1ab104c9086c39e6eaa5cab8a36ff553",
            "variant_version_id": "lrzv_f40d76f6df22e368fb8ecb6c"
          },
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "target_block_id": "lrtb_941a05450c344ce7053f357c",
          "text": {
            "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
            "qa_status": "passed",
            "text": "[!TASK]\n选择角色精灵。添加一个新脚本，使其在玩家按下空格键时向上滑行。\nGiga Walking 精灵。{:width=\"100px\" height=\"100px\" style=\"object-fit: contain;\"}\nblocks3\n+当按下 [space v] 键\n+在 (0.3) 秒内滑行到 x: (-100) y: (80)\n使用与角色起始位置相同的 x 位置。为跳跃最高点选择一个更高的 y 位置。示例角色从 x: -100, y: -70 开始，并跳到 y: 80。",
            "text_hash": "c29048b17d6645a2ce50efa45d82f27c170f3ed93019f507557ec211a3432017",
            "variant_version_id": "lrzv_f40d76f6df22e368fb8ecb6c"
          },
          "type": "quotation"
        },
        {
          "target_block_id": "lrtb_fd4fdc0a530147435cc908db",
          "text": {
            "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
            "qa_status": "passed",
            "text": "[!TASK]\n添加另一个滑行积木，让角色落地。\nGiga Walking 精灵。{:width=\"100px\" height=\"100px\" style=\"object-fit: contain;\"}\nblocks3\n当按下 [space v] 键\n在 (0.3) 秒内滑行到 x: (-100) y: (80)\n+在 (0.7) 秒内滑行到 x: (-100) y: (-70)\n最终的 x 和 y 值必须与绿旗脚本中角色的起始位置相匹配。",
            "text_hash": "a6a10c3f088dc4fb210f6914e71c11091395c08be226f8bcc230b340710a29a9",
            "variant_version_id": "lrzv_f40d76f6df22e368fb8ecb6c"
          },
          "type": "quotation"
        },
        {
          "target_block_id": "lrtb_e813a42ac2763529dc59eb8f",
          "text": {
            "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
            "qa_status": "passed",
            "text": "[!TASK]\n**测试你的项目。** 按下空格键时，角色应该向上跳起并回落。",
            "text_hash": "139bd4325946ec72b70255b2cb59b96558c76d904e02381608776b59e8a835b1",
            "variant_version_id": "lrzv_f40d76f6df22e368fb8ecb6c"
          },
          "type": "quotation"
        }
      ],
